&lt;li>btn_on_url, btn_off_url: Button toggle actions&lt;/li>
&lt;li>longpush_url, shortpush_url: Button press duration actions&lt;/li>
&lt;li>roller_open_url, roller_close_url, roller_stop_url: Roller actions&lt;/li>
&lt;/ul>
&lt;p>Gen2+ devices use webhooks instead. See &amp;lsquo;shelly webhook list&amp;rsquo;.&lt;/p>



